                <td height="401" width="100%"><font color="#000000"> </font> <br>
                   <table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4"><tr bgcolor="#FFC000"><td><font color="#000000"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial" size="6">ISB Scum Ver. 2.0</font></td></tr></table><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td></td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#FFC000">Rating</Font></TD><TD><IMG SRC="images/dd9.GIF" BORDER=0><A HREF="darkread.php3?deck=2167"><IMG SRC="images/ddread.GIF" BORDER=0></A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#FFC000">Author</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Nicholas "Olas" Burke</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#FFC000">Description</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Actual version 35 of this deck, with a little better explaintions of the cards.  Please read the deck before putting stupid reviews.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#FFC000">Cards</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Locations:<br>
Coruscant <br>
Jabba's Palace: Audience Chamber  x2<br>
Jabba's Palace: Dungeon <br>
Tatooine  x2<br>
